<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="app-main">
        <section class="page-intro">
            <span class="page-kicker">
                <i class="bi bi-info-circle"></i>
                About
            </span>
            <h1 class="page-title">How Ball Insight Works</h1>
            <p class="page-subtitle">
                The app analyzes historical football data and transforms it into quick betting context.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="app-card">
            <div class="about-grid">
                <article class="about-block">
                    <h3>Mission</h3>
                    <p>
                        Provide clear, data-backed match insight so you can make faster and more informed betting decisions.
                    </p>
                </article>
                <article class="about-block">
                    <h3>Data We Analyze</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Goal timing by 15-minute windows</li>
                        <li>First team to score frequency</li>
                        <li>BTTS and Over/Under tendencies</li>
                        <li>Home and away performance split</li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
                <article class="about-block">
                    <h3>Tech Stack</h3>
                    <p>Node.js, Express, MySQL, EJS, and scheduled data refresh jobs.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="about-block warning-block">
                    <h3>Responsible Gambling</h3>
                    <p>
                        This tool is informational only. No model guarantees outcomes, so never stake beyond your risk limits.
                    </p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
